        <item>
            <title><![CDATA[湖北省原“一把手”蒋超良高票当选全国人大常委会委员]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[<div class="figure-media figure-media-gallery figure-media-gallery-overlay js-figure-media-gallery js-figure-media-gallery-overlay">
         <div class="figure-media-gallery-slide"><div class="figure-media-gallery-img"><img class="article-rotator-img lazyload" data-src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/2023-03/jiangchaoliang.jpg?VersionId=C5gq49sfzJwdk6nQ_BEF1_ptphmyCipo&amp;itok=5EHJqNfj" alt="" data-caption="北京人民大会堂现场公布全国人大常委会委员选举中，部分候选人的得票结果（视频截图）" src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/2023-03/jiangchaoliang.jpg?VersionId=C5gq49sfzJwdk6nQ_BEF1_ptphmyCipo&amp;itok=5EHJqNfj" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><div class="tint"></div></div>
      <figcaption><p>北京人民大会堂现场公布全国人大常委会委员选举中，部分候选人的得票结果（视频截图）</p></figcaption>
  </div>
